    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/cf91de02ec39c7ded63f0638aa25cd8a.webp?t=1769181852\" width=624 height=46 /></span><br><br>这是一个少女拯救妹妹的故事。<br>妹妹小灯患上了可怕的“无梦症”，<br>美少女研究员「直子」决然驾驶实验机体，执行“破梦”任务——<br><br>飞行敌人源源不断地向你射出子弹，你需要驾驶“破梦机”【擦弹】积攒能量，适时释放【幻想技】清场。Clear之后，收集到的幻想粒子可以用于升级机体，更换皮肤。<br><br>散布、隧穿、强制、读取……<br>记忆投射的反噬令她精神崩溃。<br>梦境深处出现的少女形态BOSS是？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/a9145398c23572bd553bf428020d4103.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=68 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/122a5bacd2df71de13d723c41498ea8f.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=650 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/122a5bacd2df71de13d723c41498ea8f.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>走进沉默寡言的初中生「慕灯」的校园生活，<br>邂逅、欺凌与背叛过后，收获的是绝望，亦或……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/3476173fdcfd20d2871451ab70033a71.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=86 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c30d0d8049de923aeb1bf7f659bed619.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c30d0d8049de923aeb1bf7f659bed619.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c30d0d8049de923aeb1bf7f659bed619.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c866a7783a78d051e0094afe80bc2542.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/0b8896004477e7043cf8e2dc49d18d0f.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/0b8896004477e7043cf8e2dc49d18d0f.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/0b8896004477e7043cf8e2dc49d18d0f.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/c866a7783a78d051e0094afe80bc2542.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/1a0e50d7775ac703e8f5c39b903bc90d.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/1a0e50d7775ac703e8f5c39b903bc90d.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/1a0e50d7775ac703e8f5c39b903bc90d.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏提供4种自机。玩家可以选择「直子」的【OT-A09】、「慕灯」的【OT-A09-MK2】、「瘟疫修女」的【OT-A10】或者那个【神秘少女】潜入梦境执行任务。每种机体拥有不同子弹特性和技能风格。<br><br><br><strong>对了，还可以更换机体皮肤，以女性角色的幻想形象出击。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.s