s://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/0eab8e626827717cf3b959f2fff08644.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/8d25f94f2abfb7f08ac3f6f2d3b5b507.poster.avif?t=1769181852\" width=650 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/8d25f94f2abfb7f08ac3f6f2d3b5b507.webm?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/8d25f94f2abfb7f08ac3f6f2d3b5b507.mp4?t=1769181852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/ae5f5eca26307ede37996707b13c27e5.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=41 /></span><br><strong>使用丰富的技能搭配迎战不同的敌人——</strong><br>每个关卡在挑战前都可以通过【机体修正】配置被动能力；还可以为3个【按键槽位】选择强大的能力技、蓄力触发技和闪避触发技。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242840/extras/0eab8e626827717cf3b959f2fff08644.webp?t=1769181852\" width=616 height=32 /></span>",
